                                <cell>Together $51 52 at 4s. <hi rend="italic">5d.</hi> per
                                    dollar</cell>
                                <cell role="num">
                                    <hi rend="italic">£</hi>9</cell>
                                <cell role="num">13</cell>
                                <cell role="num">2</cell>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell>For wages of two substitutes for the homeward voyage to
                                    Swansea.</cell>
